  "text": {
    "tr": "<h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;\">EKOL</h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">En Ofis Mobilyaları EKOL modeli, <strong>Toplantı Masaları</strong> kategorisinde sunulmaktadır. Makam odası, ofis ve kurumsal projeler için üretim ve montaj desteği sağlanır.</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Teklif ve numune talepleri için <a href=\"/tr/iletisim/\">iletişim</a> sayfamızdan bize ulaşabilirsiniz.</p>\n<div class=\"modulex-olcu-inline\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 18px; margin: 1em 0 0.5em;\">Ölçüler</h3>\n<table class=\"modulex-olcu-table\" style=\"width:100%; max-width:420px; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:15px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">Genişlik</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">197 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">Derinlik</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">122 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">Yükseklik</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">76 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">Ağırlık</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">~45 kg</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px;\">Malzeme</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">MDF / sunta tabla, metal ayak</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#5a6b7d; margin-top:8px;\">Ölçüler standart üretim referansıdır; proje ve siparişe göre özelleştirilebilir.</p>\n</div>",
    "en": "<h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;\">EKOL</h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">En Ofis Mobilyaları EKOL model, <strong>Meeting Tables</strong> is offered in this category. Production and installation support for executive offices and corporate projects.</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px;\">For quotes and sample requests <a href=\"/en/contact/\">contact</a> reach us via our contact page.</p>\n<div class=\"modulex-olcu-inline\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 18px; margin: 1em 0 0.5em;\">Dimensions</h3>\n<table class=\"modulex-olcu-table\" style=\"width:100%; max-width:420px; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:15px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">Width</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">197 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">Depth</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">122 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">Height</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">76 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">Weight</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">~45 kg</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px;\">Material</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">MDF / sunta tabla, metal ayak</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#5a6b7d; margin-top:8px;\">Dimensions are standard production references; can be customized per project and order.</p>\n</div>",
    "ar": "<h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;\">EKOL</h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">أن أوفيس للأثاث المكتبي EKOL ، الطراز <strong>طاولات الاجتماعات</strong> يُعرض ضمن هذه الفئة. دعم الإنتاج والتركيب للمكاتب والمشاريع المؤسسية.</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px;\">للعروض وطلب العينات <a href=\"/ar/contact/\">اتصل</a> تواصل معنا عبر صفحتنا.</p>\n<div class=\"modulex-olcu-inline\">\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 18px; margin: 1em 0 0.5em;\">الأبعاد</h3>\n<table class=\"modulex-olcu-table\" style=\"width:100%; max-width:420px; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:15px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">العرض</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">197 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">العمق</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">122 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">الارتفاع</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">76 cm</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">الوزن</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,48,70,0.15);\">~45 kg</td></tr>\n<tr><th style=\"text-align:left; padding:8px 12px;\">المادة</th><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">MDF / sunta tabla, metal ayak</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#5a6b7d; margin-top:8px;\">الأبعاد مرجع إنتاج قياسي; يمكن تخصيصها حسب المشروع والطلب.</p>\n</div>"
